The sauce is slightly thicker then the regular chicken or lamb curry.

review.reviewBody: The butter chicken is so good, Ive ordered it many times now.
I ordered Lamb Biryani  which was very bad with  less taste and more gravy. Butter Chicken  was also below Average. Huge price for the low quantity.
every item ordered was incorrect, missing, burnt, or raw/uncooked. the pakora was so off-putting that I puked and threw out what did actually arrive.
they did their best all I can ask for
